 HMD Global, popularly known as the home of Nokia phones has announced the arrival of Nokia 5310.The phone which comes in red and black colour combination is now available in all trusted phone shops and online marketplace. According to the General Manager, West, East and Central Africa, HMD Global, Joseph Umunakwe, their initiative is to revitalise the originals family has been a great success with their fans. “We have received an overwhelmingly positive reaction for our entire Originals family including our most recent Nokia 2720 Flip. We’re very excited to be able to keep the trend going with the Nokia 5310, our latest Originals family member.”